r\n<p>Nizki stroški vzdrževanja</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:12;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"POSLOVNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:238:"<p>Centralni elektronski arhiv za vse dokumente v organizaciji</p>\r\n<p>Lasten elektronski arhiv zaradi varnosti dostopa in zaupnosti dokumentov</p>\r\n<p>Arhiviranje objektov ločeno od aplikacij</p>\r\n<p>Nizki stroški lastništva (TCO)</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:13;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"POSLOVNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:241:"<p>Centralni elektronski arhiv za vse dokumente v organizaciji.</p>\r\n<p>Laten elektronski arhiv zaradi varnosti dostopa in zaupnosti dokumentov.</p>\r\n<p>Arhiviranje objektov ločeno od aplikacij.</p>\r\n<p>Nizki stroški lastništva (TCO).</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:14;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRIMERI UPORABE";s:4:"text";s:613:"<p><a title="ARHIVIRANJE IZ LOTUS NOTES APLIKACIJ" href="http://imis.eberce.si/resitve/elektronski-arhiv-dokumentov/arhiviranje-iz-lotus-notes-aplikacij/"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Arhiviranje objektov iz Lotus Notes / Domino aplikacij</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;"><br /><br /><a title="ARHIVIRANJE IZ ERP, CRM IN PRILAGOJENIH APLIKACIJ" href="http://imis.eberce.si/resitve/elektronski-arhiv-dokumentov/arhiviranje-iz-erp-crm-in-prilagojenih-aplikacij/"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Arhiviranje objektov iz ERP, CRM in prilagojenih aplikacij</span></strong></a></span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:15;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"AKREDITACIJA";s:4:"text";s:99:"<p>IMiS/ARC Server 7.1.1011 je akreditiran pri Arhivu RS kot infrastrukturna programska oprema.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:16;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"POSLOVNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:208:"<p>Večja učinkovitost dela.</p>\r\n<div><br />Večja preglednost dokumentacije in poslovanja.</div>\r\n<div><br />Sledljivost in hitrejše ugotavljanje odgovornosti.</div>\r\n<div><br />Nadzor nad stroški.</div>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:17;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:22:"KVALITETE NAŠEGA DELA";s:4:"text";s:239:"<p>Zagotavljamo kvalitetne produkte in storitve.<br /><br />Spoštujemo zastavljene roke in odzivne čase.<br /><br />Projekte realiziramo v dogovorjenih finančnih okvirih.<br /><br />Smo korektni in odgovorni do strank in partnerjev.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:18;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:241:"<p><strong></strong>Kvalitetno skeniranje in enostavno pregledovanje dokumentov.<br /><br />Zgoščevanje za manjše velikosti in hitrejše prenose.<br /><br />Elektronsko podpisovanje.<br /><br />Skeniranje iz aplikacije.</p>\r\n<div> </div>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:19;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:23:"PRIPOROČAMO TESTIRANJE";s:4:"text";s:269:"<p>Testiranje v vašem okolju.<br /><br />Možnost integracije z vašo aplikacijo.<br /><br />Vašo zahtevo za testiranje nam lahko posredujete preko <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-pošte</span></strong></a>.<strong></strong></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:20;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:224:"<p>Hitro in kvalitetno skeniranje večjih količin papirnih dokumentov.<br /><br />Učinkovito razločevanje enostranskih/večstranskih dokumentov.<br /><br />Integracija v aplikacije preko C-API, COM ali Java vmesnikov.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:21;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:23:"PRIPOROČAMO TESTIRANJE";s:4:"text";s:161:"<p>Vašo zahtevo za testiranje nam lahko posredujete preko <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-pošte</span></strong></a>.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:22;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:250:"<p>Masovni prenos elektronskih dokumentov ali digitaliziranih vsebin.<br /><br />Avtomatično razvrščanje dokumentov in podatkov v DMS, ERP, CRM aplikacije.<br /><br />Arhiviranje objektov na arhivski strežnik IMiS<sup>®</sup>/ARChive Server.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:23;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:23:"PRIPOROČAMO TESTIRANJE";s:4:"text";s:161:"<p>Vašo zahtevo za testiranje nam lahko posredujete preko <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-pošte</span></strong></a>.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:24;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:251:"<p>Centralni elektronski arhiv za vse dokumente v organizaciji.<br /><br />Lasten elektronski arhiv zaradi varnosti dostopa in zaupnosti dokumentov.<br /><br />Arhiviranje objektov ločeno od aplikacij.<br /><br />Nizki stroški lastništva (TCO).</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:25;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:12:"AKREDITACIJA";s:4:"text";s:78:"<p>IMiS/ARChive Server različica 7.1.1011 je akreditirana pri Arhivu RS.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:26;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:23:"PRIPOROČAMO TESTIRANJE";s:4:"text";s:260:"<p>On-line testiranje funkcionalnosti.<br /><br />Možnost integracije z vašo aplikacijo.<br /><br />Vašo zahtevo za testiranje nam lahko posredujete preko <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-pošte</span></strong></a>.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:27;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:159:"<p>Pregledovanje datotek grafičnih formatov.<br /><br />Elektronsko podpisovanje.<br /><br />Enoten pregledovalnik dokumentov za vse aplikativne rešitve.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:28;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:197:"<p>Kvalitetna pretvorba skeniranih dokumentov v tekst.<br /><br />Hitro iskanje delov teksta skeniranih dokumentov.<br /><br />Prihranki na času ponovnega vnašanja teksta prejetih dokumentov.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:29;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:23:"PRIPOROČAMO TESTIRANJE";s:4:"text";s:266:"<p>Hitro testiranje kvalitete prepoznave teksta preko e-pošte.<br /><br />Preko 150 različnih jezikov.<br /><br />Podprti vhodni formati: TIFF, PDF, JPEG, BMP, PNG, PCX, DCX.<br /><br />Podprti izhodni formati: DOCX, DOC, RTF, XLSX, XLS, TXT, PPTX, PDF-A, PDF.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:30;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:147:"<p>Posrednik arhiviranih objektov med aplikacijo in elektronskim arhivom.<br /><br />Integracija s katerokoli novejšo Java in .NET aplikacijo.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:31;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:22:"KVALITETE NAŠEGA DELA";s:4:"text";s:229:"<p>Hitri odzivni časi.<br /><br />Znanje, strokovnost in sposobnost hitrega reševanja težav.<br /><br />Dobro poznavanje zasnove in delovanja naših rešitev.<br /><br />Upoštevamo želje strank po novih funkcionalnostih.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:32;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:22:"KVALITETE NAŠEGA DELA";s:4:"text";s:239:"<p>Zagotavljamo kvalitetne produkte in storitve.<br /><br />Spoštujemo zastavljene roke in odzivne čase.<br /><br />Projekte realiziramo v dogovorjenih finančnih okvirih.<br /><br />Smo korektni in odgovorni do strank in partnerjev.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:33;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"UPORABNA VREDNOST";s:4:"text";s:117:"<p>Dostop do pravih informacij.<br /><br />Hitra pomoč pri odpravljanju težav. <br /><br />Preglednost vsebin.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:34;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"TEHNIČNA PODPORA";s:4:"text";s:163:"<p>Vaša tehnična vprašanja nam lahko posredujete preko <a href="mailto:podpora@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-pošte</span></strong></a>.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:35;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:23:"PRIPOROČAMO TESTIRANJE";s:4:"text";s:147:"<p>Testiranje vseh funkcionalnosti.<br /><br />On-line testiranje elektronskega arhiva.<br /><br />Možnost integracije z vašimi aplikacijami.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:36;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"TEHNIČNA PODPORA";s:4:"text";s:163:"<p>Vaša tehnična vprašanja nam lahko posredujete preko <a href="mailto:podpora@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-pošte</span></strong></a>.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:37;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:14:"BUSINESS VALUE";s:4:"text";s:118:"<p>Established technologies and quality services.<br /><br />Reliable operation.<br /><br />Low maintenance costs.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:38;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:14:"BUSINESS VALUE";s:4:"text";s:188:"<p>Better efficiency.<br /><br />Greater transparency of documentation and business operations.<br /><br />Traceability and faster identification of liability.<br /><br />Cost control.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:39;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"EXAMPLES OF USE";s:4:"text";s:1640:"<p><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="The central procurement process" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/document-management-systems/the-central-procurement-process/">Central procurement process<br /><br /></a></span></strong><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="Banking transaction approval process" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/document-management-systems/banking-transaction-approval-process/">Banking transaction approval process<br /><br /></a></span></strong></span><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="Leasing transaction approval process" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/document-management-systems/leasing-transaction-approval-process/">Leasing transaction approval process<br /><br /></a></span></strong></span><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="Authorization assignment process" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/document-management-systems/authorization-assignment-process/">Authorization assignment process<br /><br /></a></span></strong></span><span style="color: #000000;"><strong><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="Invoice approval process" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/document-management-systems/invoice-approval-process/">Invoice approval process<br /><br /></a></span></strong></span><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="Incoming mail process" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/document-management-systems/incoming-mail-process/"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Incoming mail process</span></strong></a></span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:40;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:14:"BUSINESS VALUE";s:4:"text";s:292:"<p>Central electronic archive for all documents within an organization.<br /><br />Proprietary electronic archive for ensuring the security of access and confidentiality of documents.<br /><br />Archiving objects separately from applications.<br /><br />Low total cost of ownership (TCO).</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:41;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"EXAMPLES OF USE";s:4:"text";s:695:"<p><a title="Archiving objects from IBM Lotus Notes/Domino applications" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/electronic-archive/archiving-objects-from-ibm-lotus-notesdomino-applications/"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Archiving objects from Lotus Notes/Domino applications<br /><br /></span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a title="Archiving objects from ERP, CRM and adapted applications" href="http://imis.eberce.si/en/solutions/electronic-archive/archiving-objects-from-erp-crm-and-adapted-applications/"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">Archiving objects from ERP, CRM and adapted applications</span></strong></a></span></span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:42;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:13:"ACCREDITATION";s:4:"text";s:121:"<p>IMiS<sup>®</sup>/ARChive Server version 7.1.1011 has been accredited by the Archives of the Republic of Slovenia.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:43;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:14:"BUSINESS VALUE";s:4:"text";s:248:"<p>A central electronic archive for all SAP documents within an organization.<br /><br />Viewing scanned documents directly from the SAP system.<br /><br />Your own electronic archive ensures secured access and the confidentiality of documents.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:44;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"QUALITY OF OUR WORK";s:4:"text";s:263:"<p>We provide quality products and services.<br /><br />We honor the set deadlines and response times.<br /><br />We carry out projects within the agreed financial frameworks.<br /><br />We have a correct and responsible attitude towards clients and partners.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:45;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:194:"<p>Quality scanning and simple reviewing of documents.<br /><br />Compression for smaller sizes and faster transfers.<br /><br />Electronic signing.<br /><br />Scanning from the application.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:46;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"RECOMMENDED TESTING";s:4:"text";s:286:"<p>On-line functionalities testing.<br /><br />Option of integration with your application.<br /><br />Your request for testing can be submitted via <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-mail</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:47;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:224:"<p>Fast and quality scanning of larger quantities of paper documents.<br /><br />Effective distinguishing between one-page/multi-page documents.<br /><br />Integration into applications via C-API, COM or Java interfaces.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:48;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"RECOMMENDED TESTING";s:4:"text";s:186:"<p>Your request for testing can be submitted via <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-mail</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:49;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:218:"<p>Mass transfer of electronic documents or digitized contents.<br /><br />Automatic routing of documents and data to DMS, ERP, CRM applications.<br /><br />Archiving of objects on IMiS<sup>®</sup>/ARChive Server.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:50;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"RECOMMENDED TESTING";s:4:"text";s:186:"<p>Your request for testing can be submitted via <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-mail</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:51;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:292:"<p>Central electronic archive for all documents within an organization.<br /><br />Proprietary electronic archive for ensuring the security of access and confidentiality of documents.<br /><br />Archiving objects separately from applications.<br /><br />Low total cost of ownership (TCO).</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:52;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"RECOMMENDED TESTING";s:4:"text";s:195:"<p>On-line functionalities testing.<br /><br />Option of integration with your application.<br /><br />Your request for testing can be submitted via <a href="mailto:info@imis.si">e-mail</a>.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:53;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:13:"ACCREDITATION";s:4:"text";s:108:"<p>IMiS/ARChive Server version 7.1.1011 has been accredited by the Archives of the Republic of Slovenia.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:54;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:136:"<p>Reviewing graphic file formats.<br /><br />Electronic signing.<br /><br />A single document viewer for all application solutions.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:56;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:204:"<p>Quality conversion of scanned documents into text.<br /><br />Fast search for parts of the text of scanned documents.<br /><br />Saves time by not having to re-enter the text of received documents.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:57;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"RECOMMENDED TESTING";s:4:"text";s:267:"<p>Fast testing of the quality of text recognition via e-mail.<br /><br />Over 150 different languages.<br /><br />Supported input formats: TIFF, PDF, JPEG, BMP, PNG, PCX, DCX.<br /><br />Supported output formats: DOCX, DOC, RTF, XLSX, XLS, TXT, PPTX, PDF-A, PDF.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:58;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:153:"<p>An agent for archived objects between the application and the electronic archive.<br /><br />Integration with any newer Java and .NET application.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:59;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"QUALITY OF OUR WORK";s:4:"text";s:252:"<p>Fast response times.<br /><br />Knowledge, expertise and the ability to solve problems quickly.<br /><br />Good knowledge of the design and operation of our solutions.<br /><br />Taking into account the wishes of clients for new functionalities.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:60;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:16:"PRACTICAL VALUE ";s:4:"text";s:279:"<p>Notifications of new versions of an IMiS<sup>®</sup>software product.<br /><br />Issuing of patches for an IMiS<sup>®</sup> software product.<br /><br />Advice on how to use a new functionality.<br /><br />Instructions for eliminating the most common problems of users.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:61;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"TECHNICAL SUPPORT";s:4:"text";s:184:"<p>You can submit your technical questions via <a href="mailto:info@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-mail</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:62;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:15:"PRACTICAL VALUE";s:4:"text";s:123:"<p>Access to the right information.<br /><br />Fast help for eliminating problems.<br /><br />Transparency of contents.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:63;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"TECHNICAL SUPPORT";s:4:"text";s:187:"<p>You can submit your technical questions via <a href="mailto:support@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-mail</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:64;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"RECOMMENDED TESTING";s:4:"text";s:95:"<p>Testing of all functionalities.<br /><br />Option of integration with your applications.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:65;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:17:"TECHNICAL SUPPORT";s:4:"text";s:187:"<p>You can submit your technical questions via <a href="mailto:support@imis.si"><strong><span style="color: #000000;">e-mail</span></strong></a><span style="color: #000000;">.</span></p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:66;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:19:"QUALITY OF OUR WORK";s:4:"text";s:263:"<p>We provide quality products and services.<br /><br />We honor the set deadlines and response times.<br /><br />We carry out projects within the agreed financial frameworks.<br /><br />We have a correct and responsible attitude towards clients and partners.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes');
